@DATABASE "River Rescue"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - R - River Rescue"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - R
                   ====================================

                               River Rescue
                               ============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33420,0) ZXAMPoke(33452,0)"}          33420,0:33452,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33199,255))"}          33199,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         I haven't tested this one as I don't have the
                         game :(
                                  Rastan
@endnode
